<div class="banner" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.4),rgba(0,0,0,0.4)), url('<%= image_path "banner.jpg" %>');">
  <div class="container d-flex align-items-center flex-column">
    <h1>Konnected brings <strong>tech alumni</strong> to <strong>small companies</strong>!</h1>
    <p>No need to invest huge amounts to develop your project.</p>
    <div class="d-flex">
      <form method="GET" action="/users/sign_up">
        <input type="hidden" id="custId" name="student" value="false">
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary mx-3">
          Start your project
        </button>
      </form>
      <form method="GET" action="/users/sign_up">
        <input type="hidden" id="custId" name="student" value="true" >
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-outline-light mx-3">
          Register as student
        </button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container my-4 d-flex align-items-center flex-column">
  <div class="card-homepage shadow p-4 mb-5 col-10">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-12 col-md-2 feature-col mt-2">
        <i class="fas fa-laptop-code feature-home"></i>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-md-10">
        <h2>Fully personalized website</h2>
        <p>Everything is up to you, but we are there to support you from the beginning to the end. <br>
        When creating your project, we will ask you which pages and features you need for your website. <br>
        If you don't know where to start, take a look at our article <a href="#">How do I know what I need for my website?</a> </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card-homepage shadow p-4 mb-5 col-10">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-12 col-md-2 feature-col mt-2">
        <i class="far fa-comments feature-home"></i>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-md-10">
        <h2>Real time updates</h2>
        <p>Your developer will show you the updates after each feature implementation so that you can
        have an overview of the project at any point in time. <br>
        Communication is key, this is why the platform has a whole communication tool implemented.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card-homepage shadow p-4 mb-5 col-10">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-12 col-md-2 feature-col mt-2">
        <i class="far fa-check-square feature-home"></i>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-md-10">
        <h2>Money back guarantee</h2>
        <p>When starting working on your project, your developer will develop a prototype to show you what the application will look like
        and what the features will do.<br>
        If you are not satisfied with the final project, our team will compare the final results with the prototype you agreed on. <br>
        Our student will continue working on the project until the final results are satisfying all the needs listed in the prototype.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>